Resource Profile: Legemiddel

Official URL: http://hl7.no/fhir/ig/lmdi/StructureDefinition/lmdi-medication Version: 1.0.7
Draft as of 2025-09-30 Computable Name: Legemiddel

Beskrivelse av legemiddel.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: Legemiddel, Legemiddeladministrering and Legemiddelrekvirering
  • Examples for this Profile: Medication/Medisin-1-LegemiddelDose-Oxycodone, Medication/Medisin-2-Paracetamol and Medication/Medisin-3-LegemiddelPakning-Monoket
